    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What would happen if crows evolved further than apes?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Crowded, a dynamic avian citybuilder where you’re tasked with building a society in the sky. As a cunning crow you’ll need every tool at your disposal and plenty of wiles to keep the flock safe, fed and happy. After all, there’s no ‘i’ in Murder!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282600/extras/6401d3b5e9aa7bf0cfcbb91d5e4f0d57.poster.avif?t=1762761974\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282600/extras/6401d3b5e9aa7bf0cfcbb91d5e4f0d57.webm?t=1762761974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282600/extras/6401d3b5e9aa7bf0cfcbb91d5e4f0d57.mp4?t=1762761974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scavenge for delicious bugs and building materials, managing resources wisely so your feathered friends get what they need. Take flight and explore a landscape of lush forests and sprawling meadows, planting new trees to expand your territory. Strategically design your nest-city to support and shelter your flock. As you innovate, you’ll also evolve, developing new skills and abilities to lead your flock to greatness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282600/extras/276b6480448fa7d431c19747f0602f0d.poster.avif?t=1762761974\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282600/extras/276b6480448fa7d431c19747f0602f0d.webm?t=1762761974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282600/extras/276b6480448fa7d431c19747f0602f0d.mp4?t=1762761974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world beyond may be dangerous, but you’re crafty enough to not just survive, but thrive. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Engineer </strong>an intricate network of crow nests!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Scavenge </strong>for resources out in the world!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Manipulate </strong>the wind for travel and convenience!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore </strong>a beautiful landscape from the sky!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Evolve </strong>as you go with new skills and enhancements!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Inspired </strong>by real life crows, this is a city builder like no other!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282600/extras/6f4c18b12c82b614a42a49bc909cf212.poster.avif?t=1762761974\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282600/extras/6f4c18b12c82b614a42a49bc909cf212.webm?t=1762761974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282600/extras/6f4c18b12c82b614a42a49bc909cf212.mp4?t=1762761974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p></li></ul>",
